      <p><a href="attorneys_eng.html">ALBA GROUP lawyers</a> have experience of successful representation of clients’ interests in courts of general jurisdiction and arbitration courts of all levels in the most regions of the Russian Federation (including the Supreme court of the Russian Federation and Supreme Arbitration court of the Russian Federation), the Republics of Kazakhstan, the Kyrgyz Republic (including the Constitutional court of KR, the Supreme court of KR).</p>

      <p>Besides, <b>legal company ALBA GROUP</b> on a regular basis cooperates with the lawyers practising in various regions of the Russian Federation, Republic of Kazakhstan, the Kyrgyz Republic.</p>

      <p>ALBA GROUP provides complex legal support of clients at various stages of settlement of disputable situations:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>a pre-judicial stage of settlement of disputes:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>working out of effective strategy of settlement of a disputable situation,
              <li>legal support of clients at negotiation within the pre-trial disputes resolution;
            </ul>
            <br />
          <li><b>proceedings:</b>
            <ul>
              <li>representation of clients’ interests in arbitration courts (all instances),
              <li>representation of clients’ interests in courts of general jurisdiction (all instances),
              <li>representation of clients’ interests in the arbitration courts,
              <li>participation in preparation and representation of clients’ interests in international permanent and ad hoc arbitration, preparation of legal opinion,
              <li>assessment of possibilities for debt recovery, and also a package plan with regard to debtor’s assets search and assistance in taking of interim measures,
              <li>legal support of clients at healing measures,
              <li>legal support at enforcement proceedings,
              <li>Clients’ advice on all issues relating to consideration of disputes in a judicial procedure;
            </ul>
            <br />
          <li><b>исполнение иностранных арбитражных и судебных решений в России и странах СНГ, а также исполнения решений арбитражных и третейских судов России и стран СНГ в России / СНГ и за рубежом.</b>
        </ul>
      <p>Высокое качество исполнения поручений клиентов при разрешении споров обеспечивается как профессиональной компетентностью наших специалистов, так и многолетним опытом осуществления нашими специалистами и адвокатами профессиональной деятельности непосредственно в регионах.</p>
      <p> Если Вас интересует более подробная информация относительно комплекса услуг, оказываемых АЛЬБА ГРУПП в части правового сопровождения клиентов по вопросам разрешения споров, то уточнить любые вопросы Вы можете по координатам, указанным на странице <a href='contacts_eng.html'>Контакты</a>.</p>
